Question: a pair of warthogs are facing each other with noses touching

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many warthogs are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many warthogs are in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are the warthogs facing each other?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are the warthogs facing each other?')
ANSWER4=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are the warthogs touching noses?')
ANSWER5=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are the warthogs touching noses?')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == 2 and {ANSWER2} and {ANSWER4}')
ANSWER7=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} == 2 and {ANSWER3} and {ANSWER5}')
ANSWER8=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER6} xor {ANSWER7}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER8)
```
